{"tid":36362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先去寄信，郵局個女職員想呃我秤😦","createTime":"2016-12-12T15:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T18:04:27.000Z","uid":9931,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4f3365232f99acbb21d4580f665607ea021b35","tid":36362,"uid":9931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"拿就咁🤔<br />\n<br />\n頭先食完飯順路行過郵局就去寄野啦，埋到去一睇，係個廿幾碎既靚妹都覺得奇🤔，郵局唔係全部呀叔呀蟬黎既咩？😖<br />\n<br />\n咁平時有寄開我都知封信大約係$10.6，但佢同我講要$33，我就問佢：你磅多次🤔<br />\n<br />\n佢一磅，又真係顯示$33。正當我想拎錢出黎時，都係懷疑：唔該你磅多次我睇下🤔<br />\n<br />\n郵局妹妹仔：😑<br />\n<br />\n今次就$28，有冇咁能奇？😦<br />\n<br />\n我先留意到佢企既姿勢唔同左，於是打側一睇，佢原來用封信擋住，後面擺對波上磅😡😡😡<br />\n<br />\n挑!!都唔知幾多懵鳩已經被呃!😤<br />\n<br />\n有人想知再講😌"},{"pid":"d154735ad9a997a3b7a54ce91a102cd04f278c72","tid":36362,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"回夠帶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b80b5e4bbefe7d164283cdb5f88a7d4ea10185","tid":36362,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"冇圖你叫我地點樣聯想到對波大定細"},{"pid":"e4e65687c19c759c4a9ae643d163036ed3d79ed9","tid":36362,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回夠帶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb1a063f8b6b2a59f335f73ebdccd2b1bb9bff5","tid":36362,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"收手喇"},{"pid":"0d5aec1ed90870e53895044291ae33d89c181b62","tid":36362,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"想知"},{"pid":"9fe5a41a06d09c93fe37908166f7a3bf8773c813","tid":36362,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown